Package eiteam.esteemedinnovation.api.tile

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ThumperAdjacentBehaviorModifier
    An adjacent block modifier for the Thumper is a Tile Entity which modifies the behavior of the Thumper when it is adjacent.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SteamReactorTileEntity
    Similar to the SteamTransporterTileEntity, this tile entity is used for steam "reactor" blocks.
    SteamTransporterTileEntity  
    TileEntityBase
    Base tile entity class, mainly so we can have handy helper methods across all of our TEs.
    TileEntityTickableSafe
    Base TileEntity class that ensures that no tick code is executed when the block in its occupied position is not the expected one (usually, when this issue arises, it is air.)
